---
name: Database Schema
description: All database tables, columns, and relationships for AuraCRM
type: feature
---
Tables: profiles, companies, contacts (+ avatar_url, lead_score), opportunities (stage is TEXT, not enum), tasks, campaigns, activities, tags, contact_tags, segments, segment_contacts, custom_fields, contact_custom_values, channels, channel_messages, smtp_config, email_templates, email_queue, email_tracking, campaign_sends, automations, automation_runs, automation_run_logs, api_keys, opportunity_stages, projects, project_contacts, project_campaigns, project_opportunities, project_tasks
- opportunity_stages: user-configurable pipeline stages with name, color, sort_order
- projects: name, description, client_name, status, color — groups entities by client/project
- project_* junction tables: many-to-many linking projects to contacts, campaigns, opportunities, tasks
- Storage bucket: avatars (public read)
All tables have RLS by user_id.
